    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior is clean, showing only minor rock chips and a few light surface scratches consistent with normal driving. Inside, the cabin is tidy with minimal wear on the upholstery and all electronics functioning as intended. Mechanically, it remains strong and reliable, having received regular service updates. It\u2019s a solid, dependable car that presents well and is ready for its next owner.",
      "price": 36800.0,
